pull_request.title: Add releasetest
pull_request.body:
Adds release test (activating all algorithms and testing "full matrix" all PQ SIG/KEM TLS1.3 connection possibilities). To be referenced/used in [liboqs release process](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/wiki/Release-process). 

Fixes #280.

pull_request.body:
Bumps the actions group with 1 update: [KyleMayes/install-llvm-action](https://github.com/kylemayes/install-llvm-action).
Release notes

Sourced from KyleMayes/install-llvm-action's releases.

v1.9.0

  • Add support for LLVM 17 (binaries not available for macOS runners)
  • Update dependencies and use node20 runner
  • Fix downloadUrl option usage on Linux and Windows runners (#57)

  • be40c5a Use custom download URL on Linux/Windows
  • 878985d Recommend against caching
  • 54595e5 Add support for LLVM 17
